    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Blog Post 11 -->
        <a href="/blog/professional-web-design-shelby-nc-leads" class="group bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:border-brand-blue/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gray-800 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-dark to-transparent opacity-60"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-brand-sky/10 font-heading text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest transform -rotate-12">Article #11</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="text-brand-accent text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Vol #2 Article #11</span>
              <span class="text-brand-sky/40 text-xs">•</span>
              <span class="text-brand-sky/40 text-xs">June 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-brand-cyan transition-colors mb-3">
              How Professional Web Design Shelby NC Drives More Local Leads in 2026
            </h2>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm line-clamp-3">
              Local customers are actively searching for "web designers near me" — not because they want to build websites, but because they need trustworthy local service providers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </a>

